      "type": "description",
      "value": {
        "latex": "On doit placer autour d'une table ronde un groupe de $2n$ personnes, $n$ hommes\net $n$ femmes, qui constituent $n$ couples.\nCombien existe-t-il de dispositions $\\ldots$",
        "html": "<p>On doit placer autour d’une table ronde un groupe de <span class=\"math inline\">\\(2n\\)</span> personnes, <span class=\"math inline\">\\(n\\)</span> hommes et <span class=\"math inline\">\\(n\\)</span> femmes, qui constituent <span class=\"math inline\">\\(n\\)</span> couples. Combien existe-t-il de dispositions <span class=\"math inline\">\\(\\ldots\\)</span></p>\n"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "8b87dfcd-60c0-4668-a13a-98e0a175d320",
      "type": "question",
      "value": {
        "latex": "au total ?",
        "html": "<p>au total ?</p>\n"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "e7324639-53e0-413f-ae76-6a721b784b7f",
      "type": "reponse",
      "value": {
        "latex": "$(2n)!$.",
        "html": "<p><span class=\"math inline\">\\((2n)!\\)</span>.</p>\n"
      }
    },
    {
      "id": "e2890586-dd23-4f72-b3fe-2fbae8e02a87",
      "type": "question",
      "value": {
        "latex": "en respectant l'alternance des sexes ?",
        "html": "<p>en respectant l’alternance des sexes ?</p>\n"
      }
    },
    {
